\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" feature-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1396023342798\" href=\"/arts/0/26776597\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/73862000/jpg/_73862728_yp_hilliard_christopher_wise_1024.jpg\" alt=\"Miniature by Nicholas Hilliard: Christopher Wise\" />Portraits of desire</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Nicholas Hilliard, the artist whose miniatures stemmed from hidden social codes and romantic games \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__26776597\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<hr />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<li class=\"medium-image\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" feature-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1395021119233\" href=\"/arts/0/26453306\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/73579000/jpg/_73579836_fq_digital_1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Frank Quitely sketching digitally\" />Frank Quitely</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The Scottish artist has drawn iconic characters like Superman, Batman and the X-Men. \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__26453306\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<hr />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<li class=\"medium-image\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" feature-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1395276115773\" href=\"/news/in-pictures-26517457\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/73539000/jpg/_73539478_dalailamaportraitoffreedommixedmedia100x100cm.jpg\" alt=\"The Dalai Lama, mixed media \" />Freedom2014</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Your artwork on the theme of freedom around the world \t\t  <a class=\"from-external-source\" href=\"/news/\">BBC News</a>\r\n\t\r\n\t\t